13 thoughts we all had watching Gogglebox 
Irish Examiner Saturday 24th October, 2015 
A Friday night would not be the same without the insightful TV commentary of our Gogglebox favourites. And boy did they pull out the stops tonight. Laughter and joy were abound as they unpicked the best of the week’s TV.
